        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.f-secure.com/weblog/archives/archive-012006.html#00000761">F-Secure : News from the Lab - It&#39;s not a bug, it&#39;s a feature</a></h4>

        

        <p>The currently-circulating Windows WMF exploit &#8220;probably affects more computers than any other security vulnerability, ever.&#8221;  Every PC running any version of Windows since 1990 &#8212; even if fully patched &#8212; is vulnerable!</p>

