<h3 class="date"><a href="/2005/dec/28/">&#x27a0;</a> December 28, 2005</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="tunatic_free_music_identificat" >

        
        <a name="002188"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.wildbits.com/tunatic/">Tunatic: free music identification software</a></h4>

        

        <p>Shazam-a-like &#8220;hold a microphone up to a speaker and identify the tune&#8221; service that runs on your PC.  Neither codebase or database is open, sadly.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
