<h3 class="date"><a href="/2005/dec/07/">&#x27a0;</a> December 7, 2005</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="ratdvd_the_dvd_movie_download" >

        
        <a name="002158"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.ratdvd.dk/">ratDVD - the DVD movie download format</a></h4>

        

        <p>Compression/packaging format to rip *everything* from a DVD &#8212; Menus, special features, commentaries, etc.  Also allows you to unpack and burn back to a DVD!  Windows-only at the moment, sadly.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
